channel.title: Epic sword omfg
channel.description:
[img]http://i737.photobucket.com/albums/xx15/PiGReaR/yeah-2.jpg[/img]
IM TOO GOOD FOR EVERYONE, SO DONT FLAME ME. O.O
Sound familiar to almost every single post in this section ? Cmon guys, try to put effort into models, spend more than 10 minutes. Take your time. Ask questions if you need help. I know some people think if they ask questions, they wont get answered, because people never take the time. If you make a post about modeling, and nobody answers it, PM me ill be happy to help you. Just please stop making effortless models.
Cheers, Piggy.
